# PED::SET_BLOCKING_OF_NON_TEMPORARY_EVENTS_FOR_AMBIENT_PEDS_THIS_FRAME

## Summary
Blocks non temp events for ambient peds this frame.  Excludes law enforcement peds

## Parameters
* **BOOL** block
